kindred.common

Enum ClientToServerEnum

  • Object
    • Enum<ClientToServerEnum>
      • kindred.common.ClientToServerEnum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ClientToServerEnum>

    public enum ClientToServerEnum
extends Enum<ClientToServerEnum>
    Contains an enum number for every type of message that a Client can send to the Server.
    Author:
    Kindred Team

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      EMPTY
      Dummy message used mainly for pinging the server.
      GAME_ACTION
      Sends an action-related to the game being played.
      HOST
      Tries to host a new room to play on the map specified as argument.
      JOIN
      Tries to join the room whose host's nickname is specified as argument.
      MAPS
      Asks the Server for a list of available maps to play on.
      NICK
      If it has no argument, asks the Server for the Client's nickname; if it has an argument, tries to define it as the Client's new nickname.
      QUIT
      Informs the Server that the Client will close.
      ROOMS
      Asks the Server for a list of available rooms to join.
      UNHOST
      Leaves the room that the Client was previously hosting.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • NICK

        public static final ClientToServerEnum NICK
        If it has no argument, asks the Server for the Client's nickname; if it has an argument, tries to define it as the Client's new nickname.

      • MAPS

        public static final ClientToServerEnum MAPS
        Asks the Server for a list of available maps to play on.

      • ROOMS

        public static final ClientToServerEnum ROOMS
        Asks the Server for a list of available rooms to join. Each room is made of a hosting Client's nickname and the map name they wish to play on.

      • HOST

        public static final ClientToServerEnum HOST
        Tries to host a new room to play on the map specified as argument.

      • UNHOST

        public static final ClientToServerEnum UNHOST
        Leaves the room that the Client was previously hosting.

      • JOIN

        public static final ClientToServerEnum JOIN
        Tries to join the room whose host's nickname is specified as argument.

      • QUIT

        public static final ClientToServerEnum QUIT
        Informs the Server that the Client will close.

      • GAME_ACTION

        public static final ClientToServerEnum GAME_ACTION
        Sends an action-related to the game being played. The action is forwarded by the Server to the user's opponent in the game.

      • EMPTY

        public static final ClientToServerEnum EMPTY
        Dummy message used mainly for pinging the server.
